race.description: Tabtouch Past The Post Payouts Hcp (C5)
race.comment: Tough. GOLDEN KATHLEEN (6) spiked her figures beaten a nose at Bunbury and then had no luck here and did a big job beaten 2.4L. That form stacks up and she carries 2kg less in this grade. Draws awkwardly but this is winnable with average luck. FOREVER DREAMING (8) is a leader who went well at Toodyay two back before tiring late at York over longer. She's good enough and will give a bigger site over 1300m and on a quick backup. VALSASSINA (1) is third up for a sharp stable and can show more like her best. Draws better today and the 4kg claim brings her right into it. AMJAAD (4) will be more competitive than the form line suggests. She was only beaten 2.6L in a Belmont CL5 last time and maps for a soft run.
